-shell\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-hero-copy\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-breadcrumbs\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"href\":\"/\",\"children\":\"Home\"}],[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-chevron-right\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Dog Parks Directory\"}],[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-chevron-right\"}],[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Rocky Mount\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-eyebrow\",\"children\":\"City spotlight\"}],[\"$\",\"h1\",null,{\"children\":\"Dog Parks in Rocky Mount, NC\"}],\"$undefined\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-description\",\"children\":\"Rocky Mount features scenic spots like Best Friend's Dog Park and trails along the Tar River, perfect for outdoor enthusiasts and their pets.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-rich-description\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"Rocky Mount, NC, lying in the Atlantic coastal plain, offers expansive opportunities for dog recreation. The city is home to \",[\"$\",\"$L11\",\"1\",{\"href\":\"https://rockymountnc.gov/parks-recreation/\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"Best Friend's Dog Park\"}],null,\", a favorite local spot with separate enclosures and ample running room. Beyond the fence, the \",[\"$\",\"$L11\",\"4\",{\"href\":\"https://www.rockymountnc.gov/parks-recreation/parks-trails/\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"Tar River Trail\"}],null,\" provides miles of paved and natural surface paths where leashed dogs can enjoy river views and wooded surroundings. This integration of urban amenities and natural beauty characterizes the local pet lifestyle. Our \",[\"$\",\"$L11\",\"7\",{\"href\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/cities/rocky-mount#park-directory\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"Rocky Mount directory\"}],null,\" details these key locations.\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"The city encourages responsible pet ownership through clear public ordinances and community education. Leash laws are in effect in all non-designated areas to ensure safety for all park users. For owners interested in advocacy or local meetups, our \",[\"$\",\"$L11\",\"1\",{\"href\":\"/partners\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"community partners\"}],null,\" page can offer connections. Rocky Mount's commitment to maintaining clean, accessible green spaces ensures that dogs have the room they need to thrive in this growing city.\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta-row\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta primary\",\"targetId\":\"park-directory\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-list-check\"}],\"Browse directory\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta ghost\",\"targetId\":\"map-and-neighborhoods\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-geo-alt\"}],\"Open map\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"href\":\"/list-your-park\",\"className\":\"hero-cta text-link\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-plus-circle\"}],\"Submit a park\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-footnotes\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",\"Data refreshed weekly\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Data refreshed weekly\"]}],[\"$\",\"span\",\"Live availability coming soon\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Live availability coming soon\"]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-hero-visual\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-image-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"src\":\"/images/cities/rocky-mount/hero.webp\",\"alt\":\"Rocky Mount dog park